{
  "stem": "12674.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But then, when they came, they-- they were very-- it was-- it was horrible because they-- they had painted slogans with the takeover.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had painted slogans in paint, in yellow paint, all over the streets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they made Jewish people, especially somebody that looked like they were Hassidim, with beards or-- or traditional Jewish garb, they made them-- and young girls too.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A neighbor I had, she just told me two-- two weeks ago that-- that she was scrubbing streets.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they made them clean the streets with toothbrushes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Take the paint off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was-- and they-- they-- tore him around [INAUDIBLE] It was-- Hieronymous Bosch.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was a terrible, terrible nightmare that was going on all us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember in-- in-- in-- my father was a temperamental man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He had a very bad temper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He would, woo, woo, woo, woo-- scream.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my mother would say, yell a little louder.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They can't hear you three streets away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then he would say, I don't want to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he would start laughing and realize how ridiculous he was, and then there was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the 10th of November was and this-- but they're burning all the books and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember I had a girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you want her name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her name was Gerte Mark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But she was-- she had blue eyes and two long blonde braids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when my father-- they were going around, and they were taking over all the Jewish store.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever they hadn't been taken out-- over yet, they were taking out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother was-- My father said, nobody's going to come after me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he took one of the-- what you call it, a chisel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he took a chisel, and he sharpened it [INAUDIBLE] like a razor.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
